nodes.title: Daido Umbrella Holder
nodes.description: Description: Keep your umbrella on a real sword holder! Features: -Exquisite workmanship -Smooth surface, exquisite material， -stable property，fastness edge，no color fading -The stately appearance shows the samurai spirit -Eco-Friendly Product details: Material: High-density board Color: black + red One layer: 14.5*6.4 inches (37*16.3cm) Two-layer: 14.5*11.2 inches (37*28.6cm) Three-layer: 14.5*12.2 inches (37*31cm)

nodes.title: Daito Umbrella Sword
nodes.description: Description: Fight off the rain! 100% Brand New and High Quality This has to be one of the coolest umbrellas ever! Strong 24 ribs super-windproof and super-waterproof umbrella developed based on samurai Daito sword design. You’re not alone? Fine, the super-large umbrella will handle this. Product Details: Height: 37 inches (94cm) Radius: 20 inches (51cm) Material: Aluminum Alloy Tube and Pongee Control: Semi-automatic
